Title: Series: Vie et oeuvres des peintres les plus célèbres de toutes les écoles
Description: Landscape with the flight into Egypt, after Domenichino; in outline; proof before letter. c.1805/25 Engraving
Producer name: Print made by: Antoine Abraham Devilliers
Curator's comments: From "Vies Et Oeuvres Des Peintres Les Plus Célèbres De Toutes Les Ecoles", a series of outline engravings with accompanying text by Charles Paul Landon, published in several volumes c.1805/25. Plates 1891,0511.345 to 393 all belong to this series. The naem of the engraver hass not been recognised.
Bibliographic references: IFF / Inventaire du Fonds Français: Bibliothèque Nationale, Département des Estampes (undescribed)
